     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C           W@RTCD    PARM           P@RTCD  7        B:Return code
     C                     PARM           P@OPTN  7        I:Option
     C                     PARM           P@RGNB  2        I:Range number
     C                     PARM           P@FMT            O:Format
      *****************************************************
      *MAIN
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFEQ '*SAME  '
     C           *IN01     COMP '0'                      91
     C                     GOTO T@SKIP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETOF                     909192 ¦ Reset
     C                     SETOF                     939495 ¦ error
     C                     SETOF                     969798 ¦ indicators
      *
      ** First call - open file :
      *
     C           *IN01     IFEQ '0'                             FIRST TIME
     C                     SETON                     01      Set ind.
     C                     OPEN SDLENOL1               91    Open file
     C           *IN91     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  Open error
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Last call - close file and terminate program :
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFEQ '*FREE  '                       FREE PGM
     C                     CLOSESDLENOL1               92    Close file
     C           *IN92     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  Close error
     C                     SETON                     LR      Set ind.
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Caller requests first record :
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFEQ '*FIRST '                       FIRST REC
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLSDLENOL1             9390    Set file
     C           *IN93     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP             Empty file
     C           *IN90     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  File error
     C                     MOVE '*NEXT  ' P@OPTN             Force *Next
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Caller requests next record :
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFEQ '*NEXT  '                       NEXT REC
     C                     READ SDLENOL1               9094  Read record
     C           *IN94     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP             End of file
     C           *IN90     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  File error
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Caller requests last record :
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFEQ '*LAST  '                       LAST REC
     C           *HIVAL    SETGTSDLENOL1               90    Set file
     C           *IN90     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  File error
     C                     MOVE '*PREV  ' P@OPTN             Force *Prev
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Caller requests previous record :
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFEQ '*PREV  '                       PREV.REC
     C                     READPSDLENOL1               9094  Read record
     C           *IN94     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP             End of file
     C           *IN90     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  File error
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Caller requests record indicated by key :
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFEQ '*KEY   '                       KEY ACCESS
     C           P@OPTN    OREQ '*VERIFY'
     C           P@RGNB    CHAINSDLENOL1             9590    Get record
     C           *IN95     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP             No rec found
     C           *IN90     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  File error
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ** Get next available loan number
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFEQ '*KEY   '
     C                     OPEN CLOANL3
     C                     SETOF                     89                                       CLE148
     C********** *IN89     DOUEQ'1'                                                           CLE148
     C**********           Z-ADDF9NALN    WFLON   60                                          CLE148
     C           *IN89     DOWEQ'0'                                                           CLE148
     C                     MOVELF9NALA    WFLON   6                                           CLE148
     C                     MOVE F9RGNB    WRANG   2
     C********** *IN89     DOUEQ'1'                                                           CLE148
     C********** WFLON     ORGT F9LRAN                                                        CLE148
     C           *IN89     DOWEQ'0'                                                           CLE148
     C           WFLON     ANDLEF9LRAA                                                        CLE148
     C           WFLON     CHAINCLOANL3              8990
     C           *IN90     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  File error
     C           *IN89     IFEQ '0'
     C**********           ADD  1         WFLON                                               CLE148
     C********** WALPHA    IFEQ 'Y'                                             AR1070602 AR1070602A
     C                     CALL 'LENXTLN'                                                     CLE148
     C                     PARM WFLON     BEGIN   6                                           CLE148
     C                     PARM F9LRAA    ENDNUM  6                                           CLE148
     C                     PARM           NXTONE  6                                           CLE148
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   RTNCOD  7                                           CLE148
      *                                                                                       CLE148
     C                     MOVELNXTONE    WFLON                                               CLE148
     C**********           ENDIF                                                AR1070602 AR1070602A
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      ** Go to the next range if all loan numbers for the current
      ** range have been been used
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ '0'
     C                     READ SDLENOL1               9095
     C           *IN95     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP             No rec found
     C           *IN90     CABEQ'1'       T@SKIP         LR  File error
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
      ** Return next available loan number
     C           *IN89     IFEQ '1'
     C********** WFLON     ANDNEF9NALN                                                        CLE148
     C           WFLON     ANDNEF9NALA                                                        CLE148
     C**********           Z-ADDWFLON     F9NALN                                              CLE148
     C                     MOVELWFLON     F9NALA                                              CLE148
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFNE '*KEY   '                       NOT KEYED
     C           P@OPTN    ANDNE'*NEXT  '                       NOT SEQ.
     C           P@OPTN    ANDNE'*PREV  '
     C           P@OPTN    ANDNE'*VERIFY'
     C           P@OPTN    ANDNE'*FREE  '
     C                     SETON                       96    Parm error
     C                     END
      *
      ** No record found or End of file - return error code :
      *          _____________
     C           T@SKIP    TAG                             +++ SKIP +++
      *          ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
     C                     CLOSECLOANL3
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    P@RTCD           No Errors
     C   90                MOVE '*ERROR ' P@RTCD           File error
     C   91                MOVE '*OPEN  ' P@RTCD           Open error
     C   92                MOVE '*CLOSE ' P@RTCD           Close error
     C   93                MOVE '*EMPTY ' P@RTCD           Empty file
     C   94                MOVE '*EOF   ' P@RTCD           End of file
     C   95                MOVE '*NRF   ' P@RTCD           No record found
     C   96                MOVE '*OPTION' P@RTCD           Option error
     C   97                MOVE '*NOSEL ' P@RTCD           No selection
     C   98                MOVE '*CALL  ' P@RTCD           Called Pgm.err.
      *
      ** Caller requests message sent to program queue :
      *
     C           W@RTCD    IFEQ '*MSG   '                  IF 9 SEND MSG
     C           P@RTCD    ANDNE*BLANK                      AND ERROR
     C   90                MOVE 'ACO1001' P@MGID             File error
     C   91                MOVE 'ACO1002' P@MGID             Open error
     C   92                MOVE 'ACO1003' P@MGID             Close error
     C   93                MOVE 'ACO1004' P@MGID             Empty file
     C   94                MOVE 'ACO1005' P@MGID             End of file
     C   95                MOVE 'ACO1006' P@MGID             No rec found
     C   96                MOVE 'ACO1007' P@MGID             Option error
     C   97                MOVE 'ACO1009' P@MGID             No selection
     C   98                MOVE 'ACO1010' P@MGID             Call error
     C                     CALL 'ZASNMG'                     <SEND MSG>
     C                     PARM *BLANK    W@RTCD  7          B:Return code
     C                     PARM PGNAME    P@PGNM 10          I:Pgm name
     C                     PARM '*PRV'    P@DEST  5          I:Destination
     C                     PARM           P@MGID  7          I:Message ID
     C                     PARM *BLANK    P@MSGF 10          I:Msg file
     C                     PARM *BLANK    P@MGKY  4          O:Message key
     C                     PARM           P@MGDA             I:Msg data
     C                     PARM '*DIAG'   P@MGTP  7          I:Msg type
     C                     END                             FI 9
      *
      ** Caller requests DB error handling
      *
     C           W@RTCD    IFEQ '*DBERR '
     C           P@RTCD    ANDNE*BLANK
     C                     DUMP
     C                     CALL 'DBERRCTL'
     C                     END
      *
     C           P@OPTN    IFNE '*VERIFY'
     C           P@OPTN    ANDNE'*FREE  '
     C           P@RTCD    ANDNE'*OPTION'
     C                     MOVELD@FMT     P@FMT
     C                     END
      *
      ** Return to caller :
      *
     C                     RETRN
